The paper discusses the principles and framework of a learning machine, which is a type of machine learning system. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
